org.spongepowered.api.data.manipulator.mutable.common

Class AbstractBoundedComparableData<T extends Comparable<T>,M extends DataManipulator<M,I>,I extends ImmutableDataManipulator<I,M>>

  • java.lang.Object

      • org.spongepowered.api.data.manipulator.mutable.common.AbstractSingleData<T,M,I>

  • Type Parameters:
    T - The type of comparable
    M - The API data manipulator
    I - The API immutable data manipulator
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    DataSerializable, DataManipulator<M,I>, ValueContainer<M>

    public abstract class AbstractBoundedComparableData<T extends Comparable<T>,M extends DataManipulator<M,I>,I extends ImmutableDataManipulator<I,M>>
extends AbstractSingleData<T,M,I>
    An abstract implementation of a DataManipulator that deals specifically with a MutableBoundedValue. Similar to AbstractSingleData in that it focuses on a single value, it adds the certainty that the value can only accept values of which the bounds are met.
